  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. Tutorials\n",
    "\n",
    "Lava helps you to get started by providing a range of [Tutorials](https://github.com/lava-nc/lava/tree/main/lava/tutorials/ \"Lava Tutorials\"). \n",
    "\n",
    "To find and run the tutorials on your machine after cloning the source, please ensure you have set the PYTHONPATH and follow the steps below.\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 6.1 [Linux/MacOS]\n",
    "- export PYTHONPATH=~/lava\n",
    "- pip install jupyter\n",
    "- jupyter notebook\n",
    "- Open browser based on URL shown in the jupyter log\n",
    "- Navigate in the notebook to *lava ~> tutorials*\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 6.2 [Windows]\n",
    "- set PYTHONPATH=~/lava\n",
    "- pip install jupyter\n",
    "- jupyter notebook\n",
    "- Open browser based on URL shown in the jupyter log\n",
    "- Navigate in the notebook to *lava ~> tutorials*"
   ]
  },
  {
